thumb.title: 【Feng Yi English】Mystic Diva【Synth V Original】
thumb.description: SuperSoniker - Mystic Diva (feat. Feng Yi)Stream: https://share.amuse.io/track/supersoniker-mystic-divaLyrics: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Zhe7Pgh0dN7JrtEZqaZI_bvuesoFBgJxnSgY4-G1s_0/Download: https://www.newgrounds.com/audio/download/1431445My social media: https://linktr.ee/supersonikerIt's been years since I have made an original song accompanied by a synthesized voice, so I bring you this. For this occasion I have been inspired by producers like Au5 and Meganeko to make this Dubstep song mixing a spacey atmosphere and some lyrics that talk about growth and improvement. In my opinion, I feel like it's not my best attempt, but I hope to continue improving my musical style by making these types of songs. Also during the making of this song, this was going to be sung by Cyber Diva II, but after a little progress I didn't like how she sounded, so I wanted to try with a Synth V voice like Feng Yi, just by changing her native language to English, and I ended up loving the final result of all her singing. And well, I hope you like this new song.
